{
  // =====================================================================
  //  ⚠️  INSECURE — TESTING ONLY  ⚠️
  //  These rules allow ANYONE on the internet to read and write your
  //  entire Realtime Database without authentication. This is only here
  //  so the ESP32 device and the (auth-disabled) web dashboard can be
  //  wired up and tested end-to-end.
  //
  //  LOCK THIS DOWN before any real / production use:
